folder: Victory Boulevard & Glen Street, Staten Island, NY
text:
4246 Victory Boulevard, east side, about 200 feet south of Glen Street. It appears on the James Butler map of 1853 as the A. Simonson house; in 1874 it belonged to L. Morgan.

May 19, 1932

P. L. Sperr

folder: Victory Boulevard & Glen Street, Staten Island, NY
text:
Victory Boulevard, east side, at the head of Glen Street. The maps of 1898 and 1907 show the house to have been owned by members of the Koerner family.

May 19, 1932

P. L. Sperr
